This isn't just about MKUltra. Throughout the Cold War and beyond, countless "black projects" in fields like biological defense, advanced propulsion, and even weather modification, operated in facilities whose true nature was known only to a select few. When these projects were terminated, their labs didn't just close; they were made to disappear. Foundations buried under tons of earth, access tunnels sealed, buildings imploded. The landscape itself became a co-conspirator, swallowing secrets whole. The question isn't *if* these labs vanished, but *how many*, and *what unspeakable truths did they take with them*?

